1. *Pile* se igralo u dvorištu. (A *chicken* was playing in the yard.)
2. Mama je ispekla ukusno *pile*. (Mom cooked a delicious *chicken*.)
3. *Pilеti* su tek izlegli iz jaja. (The *chicks* have just hatched from the eggs.)
4. On svaki dan jede *pileća* prsa. (He eats *chicken* breasts every day.)
5. *Piletina* je zdrav izvor proteina. (Chicken is a healthy source of protein.)
6. *Pilеći* paprikaš je njihovo omiljeno jelo. (Chicken stew is their favorite dish.)
7. *Pilеći* fileti su bili premazani senfom. (The *chicken* fillets were coated with mustard.)
8. Da li znaš gde mogu kupiti sveže *pileće* jaje? (Do you know where I can buy fresh *chicken* egg?)
9. Šta misliš, da li bi trebalo da stavimo *pileći* roštilj za večeru? (What do you think, should we have *chicken* barbecue for dinner?)
10. Uzima *pile* u ruke i nosi ga u kokošinjac. (He picks up the *chicken* and carries it to the chicken coop.)